---

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Listo para hacer crecer <span class="cta-highlight">tu marca</span>?</h2>
      <p>Agenda una consulta gratuita de 30 minutos y descubre como podemos impulsar tu negocio.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/#contacto" class="btn btn-white">Agendar consulta gratuita &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/#portafolio" class="btn btn-outline">Ver portafolio</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #ec4899);
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 40%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-highlight {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    text-underline-offset: 8px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: #fff;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
</style>
